{"id":"verb_past","title":"Werkwoorden - Verleden tijd","level":"A2","icon":"⏮️","explanation":"De verleden tijd (preteritum) kent meerdere patronen. Regelmatige werkwoorden volgen groepen 1-3, onregelmatige moeten worden geleerd.","rules":[{"title":"Groep 1 (zwak): stam + -ade","content":"Werkwoorden op -a die eindigen op klinker + medeklinker","examples":[{"sv":"tala → talade","nl":"spreken → sprak/spraken"},{"sv":"jobba → jobbade","nl":"werken → werkte/werkten"},{"sv":"köpa → köpte","nl":"kopen → kocht/kochten","note":"uitzondering!"}]},{"title":"Groep 2 (zwak): stam + -de of -te","content":"-de na sonore medeklinkers (l,m,n,r,v), -te na stemloze medeklinkers","examples":[{"sv":"stänga → stängde","nl":"sluiten → sloot"},{"sv":"ringa → ringde","nl":"bellen → belde"},{"sv":"köpa → köpte","nl":"kopen → kocht"},{"sv":"läsa → läste","nl":"lezen → las"}]},{"title":"Onregelmatige werkwoorden (starka verb)","content":"Klinkerverandering in de stam — moet je uit je hoofd leren","examples":[{"sv":"vara → var","nl":"zijn → was"},{"sv":"ha → hade","nl":"hebben → had"},{"sv":"gå → gick","nl":"gaan → ging"},{"sv":"komma → kom","nl":"komen → kwam"},{"sv":"se → såg","nl":"zien → zag"},{"sv":"skriva → skrev","nl":"schrijven → schreef"},{"sv":"äta → åt","nl":"eten → at"},{"sv":"dricka → drack","nl":"drinken → dronk"},{"sv":"ge → gav","nl":"geven → gaf"},{"sv":"ta → tog","nl":"nemen → nam"}]}],"exercises":[{"type":"fill_blank","question":"Igår ___ jag svenska. (spreken - talade?)","answer":"talade","options":["talar","talade","talat","tala"],"explanation":"Groep 1: tala → talade (verleden tijd)"},{"type":"fill_blank","question":"Hon ___ trött. (zijn - vara, verleden tijd)","answer":"var","options":["är","var","vara","vore"],"explanation":"vara → var (onregelmatig)"},{"type":"fill_blank","question":"Vi ___ middag klockan sex. (eten - äta)","answer":"åt","options":["äter","åt","ätade","ätat"],"explanation":"äta → åt (onregelmatig, klinkerverandering)"},{"type":"fill_blank","question":"Han ___ till jobbet. (gaan - gå)","answer":"gick","options":["går","gick","gångde","gick"],"explanation":"gå → gick (onregelmatig)"},{"type":"multiple_choice","question":"Wat is de verleden tijd van 'skriva' (schrijven)?","answer":"skrev","options":["skrivde","skrev","skrivade","skrivet"],"explanation":"skriva → skrev (onregelmatig, sterk werkwoord)"},{"type":"translate","question":"Vertaal: 'Gisteren dronk ik koffie' (dricka → drack)","answer":"Igår drack jag kaffe","hint":"igår = gisteren, dricka → drack"}]}